              {
                "id": "gallery_character54699",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/77454259/51e7aa8a251b883c2b3cec352e990381_799480660810067425.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Sorush</span> can use her power to awaken the power of Khvarena that flows within the <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">thorny branches</span>.</p><p>After using this power to disperse the purple mist, the manifestation of defilement within will make itself known...</p>",
