                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/77454259/f3c7596edb7d0a09484e924bfb0a4d5a_7673761136162693487.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>The defiled entities that lie concealed within the bog are the source of the purple mist. Only by destroying them can the mist be parted.</p><p>Normal attacks do not work against them, and only the <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">power of the Nirodha Fruits</span> can completely purify them.</p>",
